---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy" description="SmallBizCalc privacy policy — how we handle your data, cookies, and advertising."
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Home', href: '/' }, { name: 'Privacy Policy' }]}>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">Last updated: March 3, 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>SmallBizCalc collects minimal data. We use privacy-focused analytics (Umami) that does not use cookies and does not collect personally identifiable information. We track page views, referral sources, and device types in aggregate form only.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
      <p>SmallBizCalc does not set first-party cookies. However, third-party services used on this site may set cookies:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> uses cookies to serve ads based on your visits to this and other websites. Google's DoubleClick cookie enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your browsing patterns.</li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> may set security cookies (e.g., <code>__cf_bm</code>) to distinguish humans from bots.</li>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics (GA4)</strong> uses cookies to measure website traffic and usage patterns. Data is processed by Google in accordance with their privacy policy.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Your browser's light/dark theme preference is stored in localStorage, which never leaves your device.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">Advertising</h2>
      <p>We display advertisements through <strong>Google AdSense</strong>. Google and its advertising partners may use cookies and web beacons to serve ads based on your prior visits to this and other websites. This includes:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>Google's use of the DoubleClick cookie for ad serving</li>
        <li>Third-party vendors and ad networks serving ads on this site</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>. You can also opt out of third-party vendor cookies at <a href="https://optout.aboutads.info/" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">aboutads.info</a>. For a full list of Google's ad technology providers, visit <a href="https://support.google.com/adsense/answer/9012903" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's ad technology providers page</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">Data Processing</h2>
      <p>All tools and calculations on SmallBizCalc run entirely in your browser. No user inputs are transmitted to our servers or any third party.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — CDN, security, and hosting (<a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
        <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — advertising (<a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — traffic measurement (<a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
        <li><strong>Umami</strong> — privacy-focused, cookie-free analytics (<a href="https://umami.is/privacy" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Umami Privacy</a>)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Under GDPR, CCPA, and similar privacy regulations, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>Know what data is collected about you</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Opt out of personalized advertising (see Advertising section above)</li>
        <li>Use browser privacy features or ad blockers to limit tracking</li>
      </ul>
      <p>If you are in the European Economic Area (EEA), you may be presented with a consent dialog for personalized advertising in compliance with GDPR. California residents may opt out of the sale of personal information under CCPA.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>SmallBizCalc does not knowingly collect information from children under 13.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)]">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this privacy policy can be directed to <a href="mailto:privacy@smallbizcalc.com" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">privacy@smallbizcalc.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
